- Solo Performance is he best of every song, fast song is to move your body. Which makes every Mummy in awe with their jaws dropping. As for slow songs, gold plated ears from the sound of every pore that is not just vocal cords. It was deep, powerful, amazing, and the Mummy gives goosebumps all over.
- Part dance is a show that we have been waiting for in the concert. Beyond words, Mummy left the it on descriptive, I cannot move on from the red pants. It was the very first exciting show that gives goosebumps and shows how professional it was. Every movement was a charm, it was flawless. So handsome!
- The sound of the microphone in the concert was a bit low
In summary, the concert was good because of the talented artist and their abilities. That's it!
Goodbye Hong Kong, hope we don't meet again!
